Class StationDefinitionList

  • java.lang.Object
    • StationDefinitionList

  • public class StationDefinitionList
extends java.lang.Object
    Class constructs a list of StationDefinition, it allows you to access pieces of the list, you can retrieve a list of Station IDs, you can retrieve Data info, check if a variable ID has is valid key, and produce a String representation of a Station Definition List.
    Version:
    10/26/16
    Author:
    Kyle Roller Nigell Mansenn
